info.description:
plonetheme.subordinate Package Readme
=====================================

-----------------
Subordinate Theme
-----------------

This is a visual theme for Plone 3. It's based on following skin:

Subordinate by Free CSS Templates
"http://www.freecsstemplates.org/preview/subordinate"

This theme is suitable for a blog or something related.
Tested on Firefox, Safari, Opera and Internet Explorer 6 and 7.

screenshot: "https://d9t.de/os/plone-plonetheme.subordinate/subordinate.png/image_view_fullscreen"

This theme was initially generated with the plone3_theme recipe from ZopeSkel and using paster.
Edited for Plone by

Niels Steurer (niels.steurer@d9t.de)
http://d9t.de


Changelog
=========

1.0 - *First Release
1.1 - Second Release with some little fixes in config files
1.2 - Added Screenshot link in the readme
1.2.1 - Bugfixed the manifest datra
----------------

* Initial release
